\c 3 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 3\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Kadhata Ganamaa
\m (Faarfannaa isa Daawit yeroo ilma isaa Abiishaalom duraa baqate faarfate)
\m \bd 1\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo, diinonni koo attam baay'ee dha! Baay'een kan ana irratti ka'an jiru.
\m \bd 2\bd* Baay'een waa'ee koo in dubbatu, "Inni Waaqayyo biraa gargaarsa hin qabu" in jedhu.
\m \bd 3\bd* Ati garuu yaa Waaqayyo, naannoo kootti gaachana anaaf in taata; ati ulfina koo ti, mataa koos ol ol in qabda.
\m \bd 4\bd* Ani sagalee koo ol fuudheen Waaqayyoon waammadha, inni immoo tulluu isaa isa qulqulluu irraa deebii anaaf in kenna.
\m \bd 5\bd* Ani nan ciisa, nan rafa, Waaqayyo waan ol na qabuuf deebi'ee nan dammaqa.
\m \bd 6\bd* Ani warra kumaatama ana irratti ka'anii na marsan hin sodaadhu.
\m \bd 7\bd* Ka'i yaa Waaqayyo, na gargaari yaa gooftaa ko! Ati diinota koo hundumaa mangaagaa in rukutta, ilkaan warra jal'ootaas in caccabsita.
\m \bd 8\bd* Gargaarsi Waaqayyo bira jira; eebbi kee saba kee irra haa jiraatu!
\b 
